originalText.text: I did not like the service here & salesmen were not inviting. This place is very expensive compared to other furniture-store businesses on the same strip. There was one couch in particular I really liked and they stated it was $1,100.00. I walked into “Mueblerias” further down the street and found the same exact couch for $650.00. The mark up at this place is crazy. Definitely do research and compare before purchasing.
